info.title: XigniteBATSRealTime
info.description: Provides real-time access to BATS market data.

post.description: Returns a set of bars for a stock and a time range during the trading day.
Returns real time stock quote for a given stock ticker
Returns a collection of real time stock quotes for a comma-separated list of stock quotes.
Returns a collection of real time stock quotes for a comma-separated list of stock quotes.
Returns a real-time quote for a security based on the last trade execution.
Returns all symbols and names that are traded recently
Returns a single bar for a specific time.
Returns a set of partial bars for a stock and a time range during the trading day.

GetBarsOutput.example:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
 <soapenv:Body>
  <tns:GetBarsResponse xmlns:tns="http://www.xignite.com/services/">
   <tns:GetBarsResult>
    <tns:Outcome><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:Outcome>
    <tns:Message>string</tns:Message>
    <tns:Identity>string</tns:Identity>
    <tns:Delay><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Delay>
    <tns:Security>
     <tns:CIK>string</tns:CIK>
     <tns:CUSIP>string</tns:CUSIP>
     <tns:Symbol>string</tns:Symbol>
     <tns:ISIN>string</tns:ISIN>
     <tns:Valoren>string</tns:Valoren>
     <tns:Name>string</tns:Name>
     <tns:Market>string</tns:Market>
     <tns:MarketIdentificationCode>string</tns:MarketIdentificationCode>
     <tns:MostLiquidExchange><!-- mandatory -->true</tns:MostLiquidExchange>
     <tns:CategoryOrIndustry>string</tns:CategoryOrIndustry>
    </tns:Security>
    <tns:Bars>
     <tns:Bar><!-- between zero and unlimited repetitions of this element -->
      <tns:StartDate>string</tns:StartDate>
      <tns:StartTime>string</tns:StartTime>
      <tns:EndDate>string</tns:EndDate>
      <tns:EndTime>string</tns:EndTime>
      <tns:UTCOffset><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:UTCOffset>
      <tns:Open><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Open>
      <tns:High><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:High>
      <tns:Low><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Low>
      <tns:Close><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Close>
      <tns:Volume><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Volume>
      <tns:Trades><!-- mandatory -->3</tns:Trades>
      <tns:TWAP><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:TWAP>
      <tns:VWAP><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:VWAP>
     </tns:Bar>
    </tns:Bars>
   </tns:GetBarsResult>
  </tns:GetBarsResponse>
 </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>

GetChartBarsInput.example:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
 <soapenv:Header>
  <wsse:Security xmlns:wsse="http://docs.oasis-open.org/wss/2004/01/oasis-200401-wss-wssecurity-secext-1.0.xsd" xmlns:wsu="http://docs.oasis-open.org/wss/2004/01/oasis-200401-wss-wssecurity-utility-1.0.xsd">
   <wsse:UsernameToken>
    <wsse:Username>string</wsse:Username>
    <wsse:Password>string</wsse:Password>
    <wsse:Nonce EncodingType="string">string</wsse:Nonce>
    <wsu:Created>string</wsu:Created>
   </wsse:UsernameToken>
   <wsu:Timestamp wsu:Id="string">
    <wsu:Created>string</wsu:Created>
    <wsu:Expires>string</wsu:Expires>
   </wsu:Timestamp>
  </wsse:Security>
  <tns:Header xmlns:tns="http://www.xignite.com/services/">
   <tns:Username>string</tns:Username>
   <tns:Password>string</tns:Password>
   <tns:Tracer>string</tns:Tracer>
  </tns:Header>
 </soapenv:Header>
 <soapenv:Body>
  <tns:GetChartBars xmlns:tns="http://www.xignite.com/services/"><!-- mandatory -->
   <tns:Identifier>string</tns:Identifier>
   <tns:IdentifierType><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:IdentifierType>
   <tns:StartTime>string</tns:StartTime>
   <tns:EndTime>string</tns:EndTime>
   <tns:Precision>string</tns:Precision>
   <tns:Period><!-- mandatory -->3</tns:Period>
   <tns:AdjustmentMethod>string</tns:AdjustmentMethod>
   <tns:IncludeExtended><!-- mandatory -->true</tns:IncludeExtended>
  </tns:GetChartBars>
 </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>
